Haɗarin cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Ƙididdigar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU/EAEA da United Kingdom wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da bambancin yanayi a kowace ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci, da kuma cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani ya kamata su kasance a shirye don samun damar yin amfani da su don karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 da za su buƙaci kula da lafiya, musamman kula da marasa lafiya.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu da ba a san asalin su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa kwayar cutar ta zama sabon kwayar cutar da yanzu ake kira SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa ana kiranta da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida ya zuwa yanzu ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna da cutar mai laushi, wato, kamuwa da cutar huhu tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan sun warke.
A cikin kimanin kashi 14 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar, COVID-19 ya zama mai tsanani kuma ya buƙaci a kula da su a asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar suka kamu da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Adadin mutanen da suka mutu daga COVID-19 a asibiti ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun yi nazarin yanayin yanayin cutar COVID-19 na ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Burtaniya kuma mun gwada su da abin da ya faru a lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK tare da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Rahoton COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 yana da ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa kuma yanayin COVID-19 a sauran duniya yanzu yana bin yanayin cutar a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton mutanen Turai na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon kamuwa da cutar guda uku a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris 2020, an gano COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK), tsakanin 31 ga Disamba 2019 da 15 ga Maris 2020 tare da wannan kwanan wata, akwai rahotanni 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun ƙididdigar tarawa da kuma tara abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin COVID-19 da aka ruwaito ga kowace ƙasa a duniya kowace rana a karfe 8:00 na safe.
Ana amfani da bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, da kuma kwatanta su da yanayin Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na yawan masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa mafi ƙarancin abin da ya faru a cikin kwanaki 14, don haka ya haɗa da yanayin tafiya na COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin da aka sanar da kowace ƙasa har zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020 a karfe 8:00 idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a cikin lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Matsakaicin abin da ya faru na kwanaki 14 na ƙarshe na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya ya bi yanayin lardin Hubei (Cina) (Hotuna 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, yawan abubuwan da ke tattare da COVID-19 ya fara tashi a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya tashi sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Karin bayani).
Wannan yanayin yana da yawa saboda saurin karuwar adadin da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK suna nuna irin wannan yanayin na karuwar cutar COVID-19 (Sakamakon bincike).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu cutar a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris 2020.
Bayanan sun nuna cewa, ya zuwa 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00, sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da UK sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin da ya yi daidai da na Italiya a makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin wadanda suka kamu da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito ya karu cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Abubuwan da aka lura a cikin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar tana ƙaruwa a irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya kasance ba tare da la'akari da bambancin matakan da ƙasashe ke fuskanta ba, bambancin martanin lafiyar jama'a, da kuma yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar shari'a tsakanin ƙasashe da bambancin ladabi don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da gwajin bi da bi.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan Italiya da ke fama da cutar sun bayyana cewa kimanin kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani a yankin sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanan karɓar COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko naúrar kulawa mai tsanani a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ana buƙatar tattara bayanai a cikin tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da kuma mutuwar.
Nazarin da aka gudanar a 2010-2011 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa dangane da samun gadaje na kulawa da kulawa da kulawa a Turai, wanda ya kai daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da ko ƙasa da Italiya (12,5 na kula da lafiya da gadaje na kulawa da juna a kowace 100,000 na jama'a a cikin 2010-2011).
Halin da aka tsara game da wadatar ƙarfin kiwon lafiya, tare da ƙididdigar yawan cutar COVID-19 na asibiti ga kowane ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK waɗanda ke da haɗarin > 90% na wuce ƙarfin ƙarfin gado na ICU, an bayar da su a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC na saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Saboda har yanzu ana clustering lamura a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da kuma ICUs yawanci suna ba da sabis na yanki na yanki, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da lamura da wuraren kula da lafiya a matakin Sunan Yankin yanki don ƙididdiga 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana tasowa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, jihohi, asibitoci, da kuma dakunan kula da marasa lafiya na bukatar su shirya don yanayin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar kula da lafiya, musamman kula da marasa lafiya na musamman, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da abin ya shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon saurin binciken haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, aiki, da kuma cikakken tsarin yana da mahimmanci don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga tsarin hanawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, saboda saurin karuwar adadin lamura, kamar yadda aka zata, bazai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci ba don fahimta, yarda, da daidaitawa da amsa mai kyau idan ba a yi amfani da shi ba a baya.
Wannan saurin tantance haɗarin ya kuma ba da shawarar matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai karancin lokaci a lokacin da kasashe za su iya ƙara yawan matakan da suke dauka na rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba a kan kula da lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, sauran tsarin kiwon lafiya na EU/EEA na iya fuskantar hauhawar marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ake samu sakamakon cutar sankarar bargo mai saurin tashi 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya zuwa yanzu ya hallaka sama da mutane 3,000 kuma ya harbi sama da mutane 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar dai kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da cutar SARS a cikin dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama ana watsa shi ne daga jemage kuma yana haifar da alamomi iri ɗaya ta hanyar irin wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan ƙarancin cuta da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma ya fi kamuwa da kuma ya shafi tsofaffi fiye da matasa, da kuma maza fiye da mata.
