An kiyasta matsakaicin lokacin kwanciyar SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance kwanaki 1-14, mafi yawa kwanaki 3-7 bisa ga nazarin 425 na farko a Wuhan.
Amma, wani bincike na 1,099 ya nuna cewa matsakaicin lokacin da ake yi wa cutar ne na kwana 3 kuma yana daga 0 zuwa 24.
Nazarin da aka yi kwanan nan, kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, ya nuna cewa lokacin incubation na kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) bisa ga yawan mutane 8,866 na shari'ar.
Yana da muhimmanci hukumomin lafiya su daidaita lokacin da ake bukatar a keɓe mutane don ya dace da lokacin da cutar ta fara kamawa don hana mutanen da ke da cutar, amma ba su da alamun cutar, su yaɗa cutar ga wasu.
A matsayina na al'ada, mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ko kuma suka kamu da cutar ana bukatar su killace kansu na tsawon kwanaki 14.
Ya kamata a tsawaita lokacin killacewar zuwa kwanaki 24?
Zazzabi yana da alamun farko da na farko na COVID-19, tare da ko ba tare da alamun bayyanar ba kamar tari mai bushewa, ƙarancin numfashi, ciwon tsoka, ciwon makogwaro, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, ƙonewa, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya, da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna fuskantar rashin barci da/ko rashin jini a mako guda bayan sun kamu da cutar.
A cikin mafi munin yanayi, cututtukan marasa lafiya suna ci gaba da sauri zuwa cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtukan cututtuka, damuwa mai tsanani, asidosis na rayuwa, da kuma coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, ko da ba tare da wata cuta ta hoto ba, ya kamata a gwada su don gano cutar da wuri.
Nazarin yanayin jama'a a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan alamun cutar ya kai kashi 98% na zazzaɓi, 76% na tari mai bushewa, 55% na dyspnea, da 3% na zawo; 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin ventilator.
An samu irin wannan sakamakon a wasu bincike biyu da aka yi kwanan nan, wato bincike a kan iyali da kuma wanda aka yi a kan mutane da ba su da lafiya.
A kwatankwacin haka, nazarin alƙalumma a cikin 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiya na MERS-CoV suma suna da zazzaɓi (98%), tari mai bushewa (47%), da kuma dyspnea (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun.
Duk da haka, kashi 80% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin iska, fiye da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma ya dace da yawan mutuwar MERS fiye da COVID-19.
An kuma lura da zawo (26%) da kuma ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, zazzabi (99%-100%), tari mai bushe (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), diarrhea (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) an nuna su a matsayin manyan alamun kuma ana buƙatar tallafin iska don kusan 14%-20% na marasa lafiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, yawan mutuwar daga COVID-19 ya kai kashi 2 cikin ɗari, kuma adadin mutanen da aka tabbatar da sun kamu da cutar ya kai 66,576 a duniya.
A cikin watan Nuwamba 2002, mutuwar SARS ta kai kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutane 8,096 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
Ga MERS, bisa ga binciken alƙaluma a watan Yuni 2012, mutuwar ta kai kashi 37% na mutane 2,494 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
Nazarin da ya gabata ya ba da rahoton cewa R0 na SARS-CoV-2 ya kai 6.47 tare da tazarar amincewa (CI) na 95% na 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya kai 2 zuwa 4 kawai.
