Waɗannan lambobin sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da saurin yaduwa fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma ba kamar MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV ba.
Saboda haka, ƙalubalen da ke tattare da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ya fi na MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Sau da yawa ana samun garkuwa a cikin iyali ko kuma a cikin ƙungiya ko a cikin abin hawa kamar jirgin ruwa.
Marasa lafiya sau da yawa suna da tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan ko wasu yankuna da abin ya shafa ko hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar ko marasa lafiya a cikin makonni biyu da suka gabata kafin kamuwa da cutar.
Koyaya, an bayar da rahoton cewa mutane na iya ɗaukar kwayar cutar ba tare da nuna alamun cutar ba fiye da makonni biyu kuma marasa lafiya da aka sallama daga asibiti na iya ɗaukar kwayar cutar. Wannan ya haifar da taka tsantsan don ƙara lokacin keɓewa.
A farkon, marasa lafiya suna da ƙarancin ƙwayoyin farin jini na jijiyoyin jini (musamman lymphocytes) na al'ada ko raguwa.
Misali, an gano lymphopenia tare da adadin ƙwayoyin farin jini < 4×109/L, wanda ya haɗa da adadin lymphocytes < 1×109/L, da kuma aspartate aminotransferase da kuma ƙimar cutar viremia a cikin marasa lafiya 1,099 na COVID-19.
Halin enzymes na hanta da tsoka da kuma myoglobin sun karu a cikin jinin wasu marasa lafiya, kuma sun karu da C-reactive protein da kuma yawan jinin jini a yawancin marasa lafiya.
A cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani, D-dimer ya karu, wanda shine samfurin da ke lalata fibrin da ke cikin jini, kuma adadin lymphocytes ya ragu a hankali.
An gano rashin lafiyar photo-thorax a cikin mafi yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma an nuna shi da hasken girgije na biyu ko gilashin gilashi a cikin huhu.
Marasa lafiya sukan kamu da cutar huhu, ciwon huhu mai tsanani, da kuma ciwon rashin numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS).
A lokacin da cutar ta ARDS ta auku, kumburi da ba a iya shawo kansa ba, da kuma ruwan da ke taruwa, da kuma ci gaba da ciwon ƙwayar cuta suna sa gas ya zama marar kyau.
Rashin aiki na ƙwayoyin cuta na I da II yana rage yawan matakan surfact kuma yana ƙaruwa da matsa lamba wanda ke rage ƙarfin huhu don haɓaka kuma yana ƙaruwa haɗarin ƙwayar huhu.
Saboda haka, mafi munin sakamakon hoton thoracic sau da yawa yana daidai da mafi munin cutar.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairun 2020, bincike na farko na ilimin cututtukan COVID-19 ya nuna ƙarancin ƙwayoyin huhu, ƙirar membrane na hialin, da kuma shigar da lymphocytes na interstitial, da kuma ƙwayoyin sinadirai masu yawa a cikin huhu na marasa lafiya da suka mutu daga cutar, daidai da ilimin cututtukan cututtukan kwayar cuta da ARDS da kuma kama da nazarin cututtukan marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
An yi amfani da RNA na SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar jujjuyawar transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) a matsayin babban ma'auni don tantance COVID-19.
Duk da haka, saboda yawan adadin karyar karyar, wanda zai iya saurin cutar, an fara amfani da bayyanar asibiti don ganewar asali (wanda ba zai sake dogara da RT-PCR ba) a China a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Haka kuma ya faru da ganewar cutar SARS.
Saboda haka, haɗuwa da tarihin cutar, bayyanar asibiti, gwajin gwaji, da binciken radiology yana da mahimmanci kuma dole ne don yin ingantaccen ganewar asali.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta bayyana yarjejeniyar amfani da dabarun SHERLOCK mai tushen CRISPR don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano ɓangarorin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 na roba a 20 × 10-18 mol/L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kwafin kowace microliter na shigar) ta amfani da sandar tsomawa a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki mai rikitarwa ba.
Da fatan, wannan sabuwar fasaha za ta iya inganta ƙwarewa da sauƙi idan an tabbatar da ita a gwaji.
Saboda rashin gogewa da sabon CoV, likitoci sun fi bayar da kulawa mai kyau ga marasa lafiya COVID-19, yayin da suke gwada magungunan da aka riga aka yi amfani da su ko aka gabatar da su don maganin sauran CoVs, kamar SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da sauran cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta (Table 2).2).
Wannan ya haɗa da maganin da ake da shi yanzu da kuma wanda za a iya yi da magungunan rigakafi, maganin hana rigakafi, steroids, plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka warke, maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin, da kuma tallafi na tunani.
Har ma an ba da shawarar yin amfani da jini daga cikin waɗanda suka warke don a yi amfani da shi a magani.
Kamfanonin ƙwayoyi sun yi tsere don su samar da rigakafi da allurar da za su iya yaƙi da cutar.
A farkon matakin, SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kai wa huhu kuma yana iya kai wa ga wasu gabobin da ke nuna ACE2 a ƙananan matakan, kamar tsarin gastrointestinal da koda.
Duk da haka, rashin aiki da kuma rashin iskar na numfashi sune manyan barazanar da ke fuskantar marasa lafiya da kuma babban dalilin mutuwa.
Saboda haka, tallafin numfashi yana da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe alamun bayyanar cututtuka da ceton rayuka, wanda ya haɗa da maganin oxygen na yau da kullun, babban iskar oxygen, ba da iska mai ƙarfi, da kuma iska mai ƙarfi, gwargwadon tsananin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani ya kamata a tallafa musu da maganin oxygenation na membrane na extracorporeal (ECMO), wata hanyar da aka gyara na bugun zuciya da ake amfani da ita don magance rashin zuciya ko kuma rashin numfashi mai barazana.
Bugu da ƙari, kula da daidaiton electrolyte, rigakafin da kula da cututtukan na biyu da na shanyewar jiki, da kuma kare ayyukan ƙwayoyin jiki suna da mahimmanci ga marasa lafiya na SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa yawan karfin garkuwar jiki ya haifar da hadarin cytokine a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Guguwar cytokine wani nau'i ne na amsawar kumburi na tsarin da aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines, wanda ya haɗa da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna sa kwayoyin rigakafi su saki manyan adadin 'yanci na' yanci wanda shine babban dalilin ARDS da kuma gazawar kwayoyin halitta.
Rashin rigakafi yana da mahimmanci a cikin kula da hadari na cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
An yi amfani da corticosteroids da Tocilizumab, wani anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, don magance hadari na cytokine.
Sauran hanyoyin magance immunosuppression na cytocine cyclone sun haɗa da gyaran ƙwayar T-cell da aka tsara na rigakafi; hana IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAK; blinatumomab; 4 siginar siginar; da kuma masu hana HDAC.
Ana amfani da magungunan steroid, masu hana garkuwar jiki, a maganin SARS don rage tsananin cutar.
Duk da haka, steroid a babban allurai ba zai iya taimakawa ga mummunar raunin huhu a cikin SARS da COVID-19 marasa lafiya.
Akasin haka, steroids na iya haifar da mummunan sakamako masu illa, musamman osteonecrosis, wanda ke shafar yanayin.
Duk da haka, an ba da shawarar bayar da gajeren lokaci na ƙananan kashi na corticosteroids a hankali ga marasa lafiya masu COVID-19 marasa lafiya.
A lokacin wannan bita, babu ingantaccen maganin rigakafin da aka tabbatar.
Duk da haka, an gano cewa yin amfani da intravenous remdesivir, wani kwayar halitta mai kama da nucleotide, yana da tasiri a cikin wani Ba'amurke da ke fama da cutar COVID-19.
Remdesivir wani sabon maganin rigakafi ne wanda Gilead ta samar, wanda aka fara amfani da shi don maganin cututtukan da suka shafi kwayar cutar Ebola da Marlburg.
Daga baya, remdesivir ya nuna hanawa ga wasu ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya, ciki har da MERS da SARS.
A sakamakon haka, Gilead ya ba da wannan fili ga kasar Sin don gudanar da jerin gwaje-gwaje a kan mutanen da ke da SARS-CoV-2 da ke fama da cutar, kuma ana sa ran sakamakon zai yi kyau.
Bugu da ƙari, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, da ribavirin an ba da shawarar su a matsayin yiwuwar magani ga marasa lafiya da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi.
Za a iya samun zawo, tashin zuciya, amai, lalacewar hanta, da sauran cututtukan bayan an yi amfani da maganin lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Dole ne a lura da hulɗar wannan maganin tare da sauran magungunan da mai haƙuri ke amfani da su.
An yi amfani da jini daga marasa lafiya da aka warkar da su don yin rigakafin cutar
Akwai tarihi mai tsawo na karɓan jinin waɗanda suka warke daga cuta don a yi wa wasu da suke da irin wannan cuta magani ko kuma a hana wasu samun cutar.
Hakika, mutanen da suka warke daga ciwon sukan sami ƙwayoyin rigakafi da yawa a cikin jininsu.
Antibodies sune immunoglobulins (Ig) da B-lymphocytes ke samarwa don yaƙi da pathogens da sauran abubuwan da baƙi, gano kwayoyin da ke da alaƙa da pathogens, da kuma hana su kai tsaye.
Bisa ga wannan, an tattara plasma daga jinin wani rukunin marasa lafiya da suka warke daga COVID-19 kuma an yi wa marasa lafiya 10 allurar.
Alamar ta inganta cikin sa'o'i 24, tare da rage kumburi da nauyin kwayar cuta da kuma kara yawan iskar oxygen a cikin jini.
Duk da haka, ana bukatar tabbatarwa da kuma bayani don gabatar da irin wannan hanyar don amfani da ita a manyan matakan kafin a samar da takamaiman magani.
Ƙari ga haka, ban da tasirin warkarwa, wasu rashin amfani da jini yake da shi ya kamata a yi la'akari da su sosai.
Alal misali, ƙwayoyin rigakafi suna iya sa mutum ya yi tsayayya da rigakafinsa kuma ya kamu da cuta mai saurin kai, wadda za ta iya zama barazana ga rayuwar mutum.
Yawan kwayoyin cutar a cikin jini yawanci ba shi da yawa kuma ana bukatar adadi mai yawa na kwayoyin cutar a cikin jini don kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Samun da kuma samar da takamaiman maganin rigakafi da sauri don yaƙi da cutar a duniya yana da wuya.
Saboda haka, yana da muhimmanci kuma yana da amfani a ware kwayoyin B daga marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma a gano lambar kwayoyin halitta da ke nuna kwayar cutar ko kuma tace kwayar cutar da ke da muhimmanci ga kwayar cutar.
Ta wannan hanyar, za mu iya ƙara yawan samar da kwayoyin cutar da sauƙi.
An yi amfani da TCM wajen magance cututtuka dabam dabam a ƙasar Sin shekaru dubbai da suka shige.
Duk da haka, tasirinsa ya dogara ne akan haɗuwa da abubuwa daban-daban a cikin dabara.
