Ganowa da aka tabbatar da shari'ar ya kamata ya kasance ne bisa ga shari'ar da ake zargi da daya daga cikin wadannan cututtukan cututtuka ko kuma na kwayoyin halitta: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihi-lokaci na SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin dukkanin kwayar cutar ta nuna babban daidaituwa ga sabon kwayar cutar; (3) tabbatacce ga takamaiman IgM antibodies da IgG antibodies ga SARS-CoV-2 a cikin magani; ko sauyawar gwajin IgG-SARS-CoV-2 takamaiman antibodies daga mara kyau zuwa mai kyau, ko kuma ninki na ninki ≥4 a lokacin dawowa sama da matakin a lokacin da yake cikin yanayin mai tsanani.
Muna iya ganin cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na ainihin lokacin nucleic acid a cikin samfurin numfashi ko jini a cikin bugu na biyu (Janairu 18, 2020) da na uku (Janairu 22, 2020).
An ƙara gano pathogenic a cikin samfurin jini a cikin na huɗu (27 Janairu 2020) da na biyar (8 Fabrairu 2020); sannan, an ƙara hujja ta serological a cikin na bakwai.
Wannan gyare-gyare ya dogara ne akan ci gaba da bincike na masu bincike don neman mafi kyawun kayan gano kwayar nucleic acid don saurin ganewar asali, da kuma samfurin na numfashi ciki har da ɗaukar jini, wanda ke haɓaka wadatar samfura daban-daban, da kuma tallafawa shigar da wasu ƙwayoyin rigakafi masu kyau cikin ƙa'idodin tabbatarwa.
Ƙari ga haka, akwai ƙarin tabbaci da ya kamata mu yi amfani da shi wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu rashin lafiyan jiki da marasa lafiya marasa lafiya.
Saboda haka, Zhou et al. sun sabunta jadawalin da suka tsara mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar a matsayin "rashin haɗari".
Hakanan tsarin ƙididdiga yana buƙatar tabbatarwa a cikin aikin da kuma nazarin asibiti na gaba.
A ƙarshe, muna sa ran ƙarin tabbaci na kai tsaye za su bayyana kuma za mu nemi masu karatu su yi tsokaci.
Don ganewar " yanayin da ake tsammani " da " tabbataccen lamari ", muna ba da shawarar bin da bin sababbin ƙa'idodi a cikin ƙasashe.
Haka kuma, ƙungiyarmu za ta riƙa sabunta littattafanmu a kai a kai don su taimaka.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar COVID-19 guda biyar, wanda shi ne mafi yawan adadin mutuwar yau da kullun
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da mutuwar mutane biyar daga COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadi mafi girma na mutuwar da cutar ta yi a rana guda.
A ranar Litinin, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton cewa adadin adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ya hada da 114 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma 33 da suka warke daga cutar.
An samu jimillar mutane 17 da suka mutu.
A wani taron manema labarai na yanar gizo, darektan IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce mutuwar ta hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr. Meerjady, mutum biyu sun haura shekara 60, biyu sun haura shekara 51 zuwa 60, kuma daya ya haura shekara 41 zuwa 50.
Ya kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan Dhaka ne.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya shaida wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Anadolu Agency cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, darektan hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengal, wanda ke kwance a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A ranar Asabar, a cikin wani sanarwar bidiyo ta yanar gizo, Ministan Sufuri na tituna da gadoji, Obaidul Quader ya ce za a dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka tsara, har zuwa ranar Asabar mai zuwa.
An fara dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a ne tun daga ranar 26 ga watan Maris kuma an shirya kammala shi a ranar Asabar, 4 ga watan Afrilu.
Har ila yau, an ba da izinin jigilar kayayyakin masarufi - magani, man fetur, da abinci.
An fara samun masu cutar COVID-19 a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga Maris, a cikin mutane biyu da suka dawo daga Italiya da kuma matar ɗaya daga cikinsu.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, an warkar da su duka uku.
SARS-CoV-2 ya halaka mutane fiye da miliyan a duniya
A ranar Alhamis, adadin wadanda suka kamu da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ya zarce miliyan daya a duniya, a cewar bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins.
An danganta mutuwar mutane 52,000 da COVID-19, cutar da kwayar cutar corona ke haifarwa.
Wannan ya faru ne a ranar da Malawi ta tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar ta farko da kuma Zambia ta kamu da cutar ta farko.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ikirarin cewa, a ranar Alhamis, tana ɗaya daga cikin ƙananan ƙasashe da ba a kamu da cutar coronavirus ba.
Ya zuwa jiya, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da rahoton 1,051,635 da aka tabbatar da cutar, ciki har da 79,332 a cikin sa'o'i ashirin da huɗu tun daga 10 na safe agogon Turai ta Tsakiya (0800 UTC) a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
A Amurka, an samu sama da mutane 244,000 da suka kamu da cutar, wanda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane 5,900.
Kamfanin dillancin labaran CBS ya ruwaito, yana mai da martani kan bayanan da jami'ar Johns Hopkins ta bayar, cewa fiye da mutum 1,000 ne suka mutu a Amurka sakamakon kamuwa da kwayar cutar korona.
A duk faɗin duniya, ƙasashe sun sanar da ƙarin matakan da za su ɗauka don hana yaduwar cutar.
A ranar Alhamis, Sergei Sobyanin, magajin garin Moscow, ya tsawaita dokar kebe yankin har zuwa 1 ga Mayu.
A matakin kasa, Shugaba Vladimir Putin ya ce za a ci gaba da biyan 'yan kasar Rasha albashi ba tare da sun je aiki ba har sai 30 ga watan Afrilu.
Majalisar dokokin Portugal ta yi kuri'a don tsawaita dokar ta'addancin na tsawon kwanaki 15; kuri'ar ta wuce da kuri'u 215 a goyan baya, goma sun yi baya, kuma daya ya ki.
Saudiyya ta tsawaita dokar hana fita a biranen Makka da Madina zuwa tsawon yini; a baya, dokar ta kasance tsakanin karfe 3 na yamma zuwa 6 na safe.
Thailand na shirin aiwatar da dokar hana fita daga karfe 10 na dare zuwa 4 na safe.
Gwamnan Ohio Mike DeWine ya sanar da cewa jihar ta tsawaita dokar zaman gida har zuwa ranar 1 ga Mayu.
Shagunan Australiya sun rage adadin da suke sayen tawul a kowane sayayya
A ranar Lahadi da Asabar da yamma, Woolworth da Coles na Australia sun rage adadin sayen tawul din bayan gida zuwa biyu da kuma fakitin daya a duk shagunan da ke cikin kasar.
ALDI kuma ta yi amfani da iyakar ma'aikata guda daya a ranar Litinin.
An sanar da wannan takunkumin ne a matsayin wani sako a ofishin ta na banki da kuma shafin Facebook na cibiyar sadarwar.
An bayar da rahoton cewa masu siye da kaya sun tara kayan saboda tsoron COVID-19 ko kuma jama'a su yi zaman kansu.
A ranar Laraba, Woolworths kuma ya ƙuntata sayen tawul ɗin bayan gida zuwa fakiti ɗaya a kowane oda.
Wannan canjin ya biyo bayan ƙuntatawa na fakiti huɗu a kowace ma'amala wanda Woolworths da Coles suka yi a baya a ranar 4 da 5 ga Maris.
A cikin sanarwar da ta fitar a ranar 8 ga Maris, Coles ta ba da rahoton cewa tare da aiwatar da wannan takunkumin na fakiti huɗu, "duka-duka da yawa sun ƙare cikin sa'o'i ɗaya na jigilar kayayyaki", kuma ya kira wannan buƙatar "ba a taɓa gani ba", yayin da ALDI, a cikin wani sakon Facebook a ranar Talata, ya kira shi "ba a tsammani".
"Kasuwancin ya yi tashin gwauron zabi a makon da ya gabata", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Woolworths.
Shagunan Costco a Canberra sun kuma ƙayyade adadin da aka ba su izini zuwa fakiti biyu a makon da ya gabata.
Don kauce wa ƙarancin, Coles ya yi odar manyan kunshe daga masu kaya kuma ya ƙara yawan jigilar kayayyaki, Woolworths ya yi odar ƙarin kayan, yayin da ALDI ke yin tanadi don ayyukan tallatawa na musamman na Laraba da aka samu a farkon.
Russell Zimmerman, babban daraktan kungiyar masu sayar da kayayyaki ta Australiya, ya ce masu sayar da kayayyaki suna kokarin kara yawan kayayyaki, amma takunkumin hukumar gwamnati ta yankin kan lokacin isar da motocin sun yi wuya.
Ya yi hasashen farashin kayayyaki zai ƙaru, yayin da masu samarwa za su yi ƙoƙari su biya bukatar, kuma za a rage tallace-tallace na musamman.
A ranar Talata, ALDI ta sanar da cewa saboda an fitar da kayan da wuri, wasu shaguna ba za su iya yin wani abu na musamman na ranar Laraba ba.
A wani rahoto da News.com.au ya wallafa, Dokta Gary Mortimer, wani masanin kasuwanci daga jami'ar fasaha ta Queensland, ya ce, shagunan suna cika kayayyaki da dare.
Ya nanata cewa, takalman wankin na da yawa, saboda haka ba a da isassun takalman, kuma idan an sayar da su, sai a bar ɗakunan da yawa a kan shiryayyu, saboda haka, ana ƙara ƙarancin kayayyaki.
Coles da Woolworths sun yi jayayya [cewa] idan akwai abubuwa da yawa a kan shiryayye, idan kayayyaki kamar su tawul din bayan gida da kuma masu shayarwa za su iya [saya] kuma suna cikin adadi mai yawa, ana iya rage fargaba, in ji Russel Zimmerman ta ABC News.
Kamfanin da ke kera kayan wanki mai suna Who Gives a Crap ya ce a ranar Laraba da ta gabata sun kasa samar da kayayyaki.
Kimberly-Clark, wanda ke yin Tissue Tissue Kleenex, da Solaris Paper, wanda ke yin Sorbent, sun jaddada cewa suna aiki 24/7 don kiyaye wadatar, a cewar rahoton News.com.au.
Shafin yanar gizo na Domain.com, ya ruwaito cewa wasu masu sayar da gidaje sun ba da takardar shara kyauta ga masu siyar da gwanjo a Melbourne, yayin da ake yin karamin gwanjo saboda masu siyarwa sun yi hutu a karshen mako na ranar ma'aikata.
Littafin NT News na ranar Alhamis, wata jarida da ake bugawa a Darwin, ta haɗa da shafuffuka takwas da aka yi niyya a yanka domin a yi amfani da su a matsayin tawul.
Shagunan da ke da ƙin yin amfani da takunkumin, a cewar rahoton ABC Australia na ranar 3 ga Maris, sun ce ba su da shirin yin amfani da takunkumin sayan.
Russell Zimmerman ya kara da cewa wasu kayayyaki ma suna cikin babban bukatar, ciki har da masks, tanning, abinci mai bushewa, sabulu don wanke hannu, da gari.
Haka kuma a wajen Australia, a ranar Lahadi da yamma, an ga wani babban shagon intanet na Birtaniya mai suna Ocado ya takaita sayen tawul din Andres zuwa fakiti biyu da suka kunshi kwai 12.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar sankara
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 mai ci gaba - cutar da ke haifar da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 - a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda cutar take da muni ba, WHO ta lura da bukatar karfafawa gwamnatoci gwiwa su dauki mataki:
Duk da haka, akwai abubuwa da yawa da za su iya sauya a wannan annoba.
Idan wata kasa ta gano, ta gwada, ta yi maganin, ta ware, ta kuma sakewa al'ummarta, za a iya samun amsa, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna da matukar damuwa game da yadda cutar ta yadu da kuma yadda take da tsanani da kuma yadda ake jinkirin daukar matakan da suka dace.
A cewar Dokta Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amirka, wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
Ya ce, a cikin wani rahoto da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, "ban da mura, babu wata kwayar cutar da ke kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi da aka gano tun daga lokacin da ta fara zuwa yanzu da ta ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taba ganin irin wannan cutar da kwayar cutar coronavirus ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin cutar da za a iya shawo kanta a lokaci guda ba".
Sabon yanayin annobar ya biyo bayan shawarar da WHO ta yi a watan Janairu cewa cutar ta zama gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a da ke damun duniya.
Darakta Anthony Fauci, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Jari ta Amirka, ya ce game da wannan annobar, "ainihin abin da ke faruwa shi ne, za ta ƙara yin muni".
A ranar Alhamis, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ba da rahoton cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar sama da mutane 4,600.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019-2020 annoba ce ta cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) wanda ke gudana kuma cutar ta haifar da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disambar 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin Cutar Lafiyar Jama'a ta Duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an sami kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe da yankuna 210, wanda ya haifar da kusan mutuwar 97,000.
An warkar da mutane 364,000.
Adadin mutuwar cutar ya kai kimanin kashi 4 cikin dari a China, yayin da a duniya ya kai daga 13.04% zuwa 0.08 cikin ɗari a New Zealand.
Alamun da ake yawan gani a ciki su ne zazzaɓi, tari, da kuma numfashi na ɗan ciwo.
Matsaloli na iya haɗawa da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon huhu.
Lokacin bayyanar cututtuka a cikin al'ada kusan kwanaki biyar ne, amma zai iya kaiwa daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Har yanzu babu wani maganin rigakafi ko maganin rigakafin cutar.
Babban magani shine maganin alamun bayyanar cututtuka da tallafi. Ayyukan rigakafin da aka ba da shawarar sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki yayin yin tari, nisantar da wasu mutane, da kuma sa ido da keɓewa ga waɗanda ake zargi da kamuwa da cutar.
Hukumomi a duniya sun amsa ta hanyar hana tafiye-tafiye, takunkumi, dokar hana fita, sarrafa haɗarin wurin aiki, da rufe wuraren aiki.
Cutar ta haifar da mummunan rikice-rikice na zamantakewar duniya da tattalin arziki, jinkiri ko soke ayyukan al'adu, siyasa, addini, wasanni, da kuma karancin kayayyaki da yawa da ke ƙara lalacewa ta hanyar sayayya.
An rufe makarantu da jami'o'i a matakin kasa da na gida a kasashe 193, wanda ya shafi kashi 99.4 cikin dari na yawan ɗalibai a duniya.
Labarin karya game da cutar ya bazu a yanar gizo kuma akwai al'amuran nuna ƙiyayya da nuna bambanci ga Sinawa, mutanen da ke da asalin Asiya ta Gabas da Kudu maso gabas da kuma waɗanda suka fito daga yankunan da cutar ta kamu da cutar.
Sakamakon rage tafiye-tafiye da kuma rufe manyan masana'antu, gurbataccen iska da iskar carbon sun ragu.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei), sun ba da rahoton cluster na cututtukan huhu da ba a san dalilin su ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 kuma an gudanar da bincike a farkon watan Janairun 2020.
Yawancin waɗannan cututtuka sun danganci Kasuwar Kasuwancin Kayan Kayan Kayan Kayan Huanan kuma saboda haka ana zargin cewa kwayar cutar ta zoonotic ne.
Kwayar cutar da ke haifar da barkewar cutar ana kiranta SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cutar da aka gano da ke da alaƙa da coronavirus bat, coronavirus dengue, da SARS-CoV. Mutumin da aka fara kamuwa da cutar ya kamu da cutar ne a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma mutumin ba shi da alaƙa da alamar kasuwar da aka ambata a baya.
Daga cikin rukunin farko na shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku sun sami alaƙa da wannan kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba daga South China Morning Post ya yi hasashen cewa wani abin da za a iya ganowa zuwa ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, mai yiwuwa shine na farko.A ranar 26 ga Fabrairun, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, tare da rahoton sabon al'amuran da ke raguwa a China, amma ba zato ba tsammani a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, yawan sabbin al'amuran da ke faruwa a wajen China ya zarce na cikin China a karon farko.
Wataƙila akwai adadin marasa lafiya da ba a ba da rahoto ba, musamman a tsakanin mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar sosai.
Ya zuwa 26 ga Fabrairu, an sami karancin adadin masu cutar a tsakanin matasa, wadanda shekarunsu 19 da ke ƙasa sun kai kashi 2.4% na masu cutar a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya yi kiyasin cewa kashi 60% na mutanen Burtaniya suna buƙatar kamuwa da cutar kafin a sami rigakafin garkensu.
Lamarin ya shafi yawan mutanen da aka gwada su don COVID-19 kuma an tabbatar da sakamakon gwajin ya tabbata kamar yadda aka tsara.
Har zuwa ranar 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta yi gwajin fiye da 3% na yawan jama'arta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa sun kafa manufofin hukuma don ƙin gwada mutane da ke da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain, da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka wallafa a ranar 16 ga Maris ya gano cewa a China, har zuwa ranar 23 ga Janairu, an kiyasta cewa kashi 86% na cutar COVID-19 ba a gano ba, kuma wannan cutar da ba a tantance ba ita ce tushen kamuwa da cutar ga kashi 79% na wadanda aka tantance.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga Maris ya yi hasashen cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi na waɗanda aka ruwaito.
Farkon ƙididdigar ƙididdigar yawan haifuwa (R0) don COVID-19 ya kasance 1.4 zuwa 2.4.
Wani bincike da aka wallafa a jaridar U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention ya nuna cewa adadin zai iya kaiwa 5.7.
Yawancin mutanen da ke da COVID-19 sun warke.
Ga wadanda ba su warke ba, lokacin da aka fara nuna alamun cutar da kuma mutuwa ya kasance tsakanin kwanaki 6 zuwa 41, mafi yawan kwanaki 14.
Tun daga ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, kusan mutuwar 97,000 an danganta su da COVID-19.
A China, har zuwa ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, kusan kashi 80% na mutuwar sun faru ne a cikin mutane sama da shekaru 60 kuma kashi 75% suna da matsalolin kiwon lafiya, waɗanda suka haɗa da cututtukan zuciya da ciwon suga.
Adadin mutanen da suka mutu daga COVID-19 zai iya zama mafi yawa, saboda ƙididdigar hukuma ba ta haɗa da mutanen da suka mutu ba tare da an gwada su ba, misali, a gida, a gidajen kulawa, da sauransu.
Data na Italiya ya gano cewa yawan adadin mutuwar da aka yi a lokacin annobar ya ninka adadin mutuwar da aka yi a sakamakon COVID da sau 4-5.
Wata mata mai magana da yawun Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka (CDC) ta Amurka ta yarda, "Mun san [adadin mutuwar da aka sanar] ya fi na gaskiya", in ji wata sanarwa da aka karfafa ta da rahotannin marasa ilimi game da ƙididdigar ƙasa da ƙasa a Amurka. Ƙididdigar ƙasa da ƙasa sau da yawa yakan fito a cikin annoba, kamar a cikin annobar cutar alade H1N1 ta 2009.
Mutuwar farko a wajen kasar Sin ta faru ne a ranar 1 ga Fabrairu a Filifin, kuma mutuwar farko a wajen Asiya ita ce a Faransa a ranar 14 ga Fabrairu.
Ya zuwa 28 ga watan Fabrairu, a wajen kasar Sin, an yi rahoton mutuwar mutane fiye da goma sha biyu a Iran, Koriya ta Kudu, da kuma Italiya.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, fiye da kasashe arba'in da yankuna sun ba da rahoton mutuwar, a kowace nahiya, ban da Antarctica.
Wannan adadi ya bambanta bisa ga yanki da kuma tsawon lokaci, kuma ana rinjayar shi ta yawan gwaji, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan kulawa, lokacin da ya fara barkewar farko, da halayen alƙaluma kamar shekaru, jinsi, da kuma lafiyar gaba ɗaya.
Dangane da ƙididdigar Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, yawan mutuwar cutar a duniya ya kai 6.0% (97.039/1.617.204) a ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020.
Adadin ya bambanta daga yanki zuwa yanki.
A kasar Sin, kimanin mutuwar mutum zuwa kashi ya ragu daga 17.3% (ga mutanen da ke da alamun cutar 1-10 ga Janairu 2020) zuwa 0.7% (ga mutanen da ke da alamun cutar bayan 1 ga Fabrairu 2020). Sauran ma'auni sun hada da yawan mace-mace (CFR), wanda ke nuna yawan adadin mutanen da aka gano sun mutu daga cutar, da kuma yawan mutuwar kamuwa da cutar (IFR), wanda ke nuna yawan adadin mutanen da aka kamu da cutar (wanda aka gano da wanda ba a gano ba) sun mutu daga cutar.
Waɗannan ƙididdigar ba su da alaƙa da lokaci kuma suna bin wani ƙayyadadden alƙaluma daga kamuwa da cuta zuwa warwarewar shari'ar.
Wasu masana kimiyya sun yi ƙoƙarin ƙididdige waɗannan adadi don ƙayyadaddun mutane.
Cibiyar Nazarin Magunguna ta Jami'ar Oxford ta yi kiyasin cewa yawan mutuwar da cutar ke haifarwa a lokacin annobar na iya kaiwa tsakanin kashi 0.1% da kashi 0.39%.
Wannan iyakar ƙididdigar ta dace da sakamakon gwajin bazuwar farko na COVID-19 a Jamus da kuma nazarin ƙididdiga wanda ke nazarin tasirin gwaji akan ƙididdigar CFR.
Hukumar ta WHO ta ce ana iya shawo kan cutar.
Ba a san lokacin da cutar ta yi tsanani ba kuma ba a san lokacin da za ta ƙare ba.
