Gwajin ya kasance yana da matsala ta hanyar kayan gwaji na tarayya da aka samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga kayan gwaji na wadanda ba na gwamnati ba (na masana kimiyya, kamfanoni, da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen Fabrairu, da kuma ka'idojin da suka dace don mutane su cancanci gwaji har zuwa farkon Maris (dokta na likita ya zama dole bayan haka).
Har zuwa 27 ga watan Fabrairu, The Washington Post ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwajin kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Har zuwa ranar 13 ga Maris, The Atlantic ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaji ƙasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ba da rahoto cewa: "Mutane da yawa da ke da alamun cutar da kuma umarnin likita suna jira na tsawon sa'o'i ko kwanaki don a gwada su". Bayan da aka samu mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ba da sanarwar gaggawa, wasu jihohi kuma suka bi sahun.
Makarantun da ke yankin Seattle sun soke karatun a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar Maris, an rufe makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya rattaba hannu kan Dokar Shirye-shiryen Cutar Coronavirus da kuma Karin Bayar da Karin Bayar da Kudin, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 na kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don amsawa ga cutar.
Kamfanoni sun sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye ga ma'aikata, sun soke taro, kuma sun karfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya ba da sanarwar hana zirga-zirga zuwa ga yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30, wanda ya fara aiki a ranar 13 ga Maris.
Washegari, ya faɗaɗa takunkumin da ya saka wa Britaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci ta kasa don haka akwai kudaden tarayya don amsa rikicin.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, kamfanoni da dama sun rufe ko kuma rage lokacin aiki a fadin Amurka don kokarin rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da barkewar cutar a cikin jihohi 50 da Gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton New York City da ke da adadin mutane 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus, wanda ya fi adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan New York ya ce dokar hana fita ta yi nasara saboda an yi jinkirin yin amfani da kwanaki biyu a kan yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da mutum 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar a New York City, kuma mutum 672 suka mutu. A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa Amurka ta sami karin mutane da suka kamu da cutar fiye da kowace kasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaban Amurka Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idojin hana jama'a shiga har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan ranar, USNS Comfort, wani jirgin ruwa mai asibiti mai ɗakuna 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta sami adadi mafi girma na mutuwar coronavirus 884 a cikin awanni 24.
A jihar New York, adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ya zarce dubu 100 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki fadar White House da yin watsi da barazanar da kuma sarrafa sakonni ta hanyar umurnin jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su hada kai da sanarwar jama'a da kuma wallafe-wallafen da suka shafi cutar a ofishin mataimakin shugaban Mike Pence.
A takaice dai, amincewa da tsarin gudanar da rikicin Trump ya kasu kashi biyu a tsakanin bangarorin biyu.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki Amurka kan dogaro da shigo da kayayyaki daga China, wadanda suka hada da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya masu mahimmanci.
An yi amfani da nazarin yanayin tafiye-tafiye don tsarawa da kuma hasashen yanayin yaduwa kuma an buga shi a cikin The Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Bisa ga bayanan da Kungiyar sufurin jiragen sama ta kasa da kasa ta bayar a shekarar 2018, mutane da suka fi tashi daga Wuhan sun fi yawa a Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, da Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney, da Melbourne suma an bayar da rahoton a matsayin shahararrun wuraren da mutane ke tafiya daga Wuhan.
Bali an bayar da rahoton mafi ƙarancin ƙarfi a cikin yanayin shiri tsakanin manyan biranen da aka fi so 20, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya suka fi ƙarfin.
An ce akwai sauran abubuwa da yawa da ba a gano ba game da COVID-19, kuma Ostiraliya za ta ƙara ƙarfafa kan iyakokin ƙasa da sadarwa a cikin martani ga annobar.
A ranar 21 ga Maris, Ostareliya ta sanar da cewa tana cikin bala'i.
Saboda dokar hana zirga-zirgar ababen hawa a Wuhan da Hubei, wasu ƙasashe suna shirin kwashe 'yan ƙasa da ma'aikatan diflomasiyyarsu daga yankin, musamman ta hanyar jirgin haya daga ƙasar da suka fito, tare da izinin hukumomin China.
Ƙasashen da suka fara shirin kwashe 'yan ƙasarsu sun haɗa da Kanada, Amirka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus, da kuma Thailand.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta kwashe 'yan kasarta daga China ba.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko kuma danginsu, tare da wasu 'yan Poland guda hudu, da 'yan China guda daya da kuma dan Indiya daya.
'Yan ƙasar Poland, China, da Indiya sun sauka a Poland, inda jirgin Brazil ya tsaya kafin ya ci gaba da tafiyarsa zuwa Brazil.
'Yan Brazil da suka je Wuhan an killace su a wani sansanin soji da ke kusa da Brasília.
A wannan ranar, Canadians 215 (176 daga jirgin farko da 39 daga jirgin na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi hayar) an kwashe su daga Wuhan zuwa CFB Trenton don keɓewa na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama dauke da 'yan Canada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a CFB Trenton.
Hukumomin Ostiraliya sun kwashe 'yan kasar 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu zuwa cibiyar tsare mutanen tsibirin Christmas, wanda aka mayar da shi cibiyar killacewa, inda za su zauna na tsawon kwanaki 14.
Wani jirgin kwashe mutane daga New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu; fasinjojin (ciki har da wasu daga Ostiraliya da Pacific) an tsare su a sansanin sojan ruwa na Whangaparoa, a arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawan da ke cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, jirgin da ke dauke da fasinjojin Kanada 129 da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, jirgin saman South African Airways wanda gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi hayar sa ya dawo da 'yan kasarta 112.
An yi gwajin likita kafin a tashi kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da ke nuna alamun kwayar cutar don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai mutanen Afirka ta Kudu da suka gwada kuma suka nuna cewa ba su da ƙwayoyin cutar an sake dawo da su.
Dangane da sakamakon gwajin, an ba da izini ga duk 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgin sama, ma'aikatan otal,' yan sanda, da sojoji waɗanda ke cikin aikin agaji; a matsayin kariya, duk an sanya su a cikin kulawa da keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye wasu dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar cutar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar, da Iran) sun aika da taimako zuwa China.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'i daban-daban na Amurka sun hada kai don aika da kayan agaji zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa na kasar Sin, tare da rukunin da suka hada kai daga yankin birni na Chicago; sun yi nasarar aikawa da abin rufe fuska na N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken rigakafi da kokarin magance cutar, da kuma kare "mutane masu haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Kamfanin Interaction ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da kyautar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura tallafin dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa China.
Japan ta ba da abin rufe fuska miliyan daya zuwa Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika tan 13 na kayan aikin likita zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da kayan aikin likita miliyan 18 zuwa China, Jamus ta aika da kayan aikin likita da suka hada da rigunan Hazmat 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na kayan aikin likita zuwa China tare da yin alkawarin karin dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafin kudi ga kasashen da abin ya shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayan kiwon lafiya da kwararru don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance cutar coronavirus.
Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kuma kayan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha, don Tarayyar Afirka ta rarraba.
Bayan haka, ya aika wa Panama kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000, da kuma na'urorin ba da iska guda biyar.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar kayan kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da ingancin abin rufe fuska da kayan gwaji na kasar Sin.
Misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwajin cutar coronavirus na kasar Sin 58,000 tare da daidaito na 30% kawai; a halin da ake ciki, Netherlands ta janye 600,000 na fuskokin fuska na kasar Sin da ke da lahani.
Belgium ta kuma janye wasu abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, da ake zargin sun fito ne daga China, amma a zahiri daga Colombia ne.
A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da wani shirin ba da agaji na gaggawa ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yaba wa gwamnatin kasar Sin kan kokarin da ta yi na dakile cutar.
WHO ta lura da bambancin da ke tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a 2002-2004 lokacin da aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin rufa-rufa da kuma hana ayyukan hanawa da dakilewa da kuma rikicin na yanzu tare da gwamnatin tsakiya "ta ba da sabuntawa na yau da kullun don kauce wa fargaba a lokacin hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Sinanci".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a matsayin martani ga matakin da gwamnatin tarayya ta dauka na hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya ce duk da cewa matakin "ba shawarwarin WHO ba ne a fili", amma matakin "yana da matukar muhimmanci ga alƙawarin da za a iya shawo kan cutar a wuraren da cutar ta fi yawa" kuma ya kira shi "ba a taɓa faruwa ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da mutum zuwa mutum a waje da China da kuma karuwar adadin masu cutar a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin Babban Rashin Lafiyar Jama'a na Duniya (PHEIC), matakin PHEIC na shida tun lokacin da aka fara aiwatar da shi a lokacin cutar swine flu ta 2009.
Babban Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce an bayyana PHEIC ne saboda "hadarin yaɗuwa a duniya, musamman ga ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaici waɗanda ba su da ingantattun tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Da yake mayar da martani kan aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa "babu wani dalili da zai sa a aiwatar da matakan da za su hana tafiye-tafiye da cinikayya ta duniya ba tare da dalili ba" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar takunkumin kasuwanci da motsi ba".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 da za a yi amfani da su don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabaru a cikin ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi, yayin da ta ambaci gaggawa don tallafawa ƙasashe waɗanda "ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar idan cutar ta ɓarke".
Tedros ya kara da cewa " iyakar ƙarfinmu yana kan mafi rauni" kuma ya bukaci kasashen duniya su " zuba jari a yau ko kuma su biya ƙarin a nan gaba. " A taron manema labarai na ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sunan COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A ranar Litinin, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da "amsawa da ya ƙunshi yin amfani da dukkan ƙarfin tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya".
Daga nan, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kunna Tawagar Gudanar da Rikicin don ba da damar daidaita duk matakan Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "mai da hankali kan martani na kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomin za su iya amfani da ƙwarewar su don magance tasirin cutar a cikin zamantakewar jama'a, tattalin arziki, da ci gaban ƙasa".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an kunna wani tawagar hadin gwiwa na China wanda WHO ke jagoranta; wannan tawagar tana da nufin samar da kwararrun masana na duniya da WHO a China don taimakawa gudanar da gida da kuma kimanta "matsanancin cututtuka da yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka tare da hukumomin ƙasa masu alaƙa da kuma yin ziyarar ƙasa don tantance "tasirin ayyukan magance lardin da gundumar, wanda ya haɗa da birane da yankuna". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "duniya dole ne ta yi ƙarin don shirya don yiwuwar cutar ta coronavirus" kuma ta ce, duk da cewa yana da wuri a kira shi da cutar, ya kamata ƙasashe su kasance "a cikin shirin shirye-shiryen lokaci".
A sakamakon barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta tura tawagar hadin gwiwa zuwa kasar don tantance halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a ɗaga darajar barazanar coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "babba", matakin da ya fi dacewa da matakin tsaro da kuma haɗarin haɗari.
A wata sanarwa, Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin cewa, "Lokaci ya yi da kowace gwamnati a duniya za ta fuskanci gaskiya: Ku farka.
Wannan kwayar cutar za ta iya zuwa wurinka kuma dole ne ka kasance a shirye", kuma ya nace cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimaka wa duniya ta kauce wa "mafi munin".
Bugu da ƙari, Ryan ya bayyana cewa bayanan yanzu ba ya ba da damar jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a su bayyana cutar ta duniya, ya kuma ce irin wannan sanarwar na nufin "ainihin mun yarda cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, WHO ta ayyana annobar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Babban darektan WHO ya ce WHO "ta damu matuka game da yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin ta, da kuma jinkirin da ake yi wajen daukar matakin da ya kamata". WHO ta fuskanci suka mai tsanani kan rashin iya magance cutar, wanda ya hada da jinkirin ayyana dokar ta-baci na kiwon lafiyar jama'a da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
Daya daga cikin halayen da aka nuna ya hada da takardar neman sa hannu da aka yi wa 733,000 a ranar 6 ga Afrilu, wanda aka aika wa Babban Daraktan WHO Tedros Adhanom don ya nemi ya yi murabus.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, dubun dubatar da kwararru na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada girmama haƙƙin kowane mutum yayin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin samun taimakon ceton rai kuma gwamnati tana da alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya ba za a yi amfani da shi azaman hujja don nuna bambanci ga wasu ƙungiyoyi ba.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowane mutum na da hakkin ya sami lafiya, wanda ya hada da nakasassu, kungiyoyin tsiraru, tsofaffi, 'yan gudun hijirar cikin gida, marasa gida, mutanen da ke rayuwa cikin matsanancin talauci, mutanen da ke cikin kurkuku, 'yan gudun hijira, da sauran kungiyoyin da ke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Hukumomin duniya suna kokarin magance tasirin zamantakewa da tattalin arziki na rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar Hadin Gwiwar Tattalin Arziki da Ci Gaban ta kaddamar da wani shiri na samar da bayanai na kan lokaci da kuma cikakkun bayanai kan martani na manufofi a kasashe a duk fadin duniya, tare da ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Daga manufofin da za a karfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya zuwa magance tasirin keɓewar yanki da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, cibiyar dijital ta ƙunshi Tracker na Manufofin Kasashe, kuma yana da nufin taimakawa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da kuma sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen martani na duniya don fuskantar ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin China ta fuskanci zargi daga Amurka, Ministan ofishin ministocin Burtaniya Michael Gove, da dan Shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kan yadda aka magance cutar da ta fara a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An dakatar da wasu masu gudanarwa na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) a matakin lardin dangane da gudanar da aikin killacewa a tsakiyar kasar Sin, wanda ke nuna rashin jin daɗi game da martanin da hukumomin siyasa ke bayarwa game da barkewar cutar a yankin.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan matakin ne don kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da cutar ta coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an China, kamar Zhao Lijian, sun yi watsi da amincewar da suka yi a baya cewa annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, kuma sun goyi bayan ka'idar da'awar cewa COVID-19 ta samo asali ne daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka Donald Trump ta kira coronavirus da "kwayar cutar China" ko "kwayar cutar Wuhan" kuma ta ce "aikin China na rufe fuska ya ba da ƙarfi ga cutar da ke zama cutar ta duniya". Wannan furucin daga baya ya zama abin zargi daga wasu masu sukar da ke nuna wariyar launin fata da kuma "juya hankali daga gazawar gwamnatinsa wajen magance cutar korona".
Daily Beast ta sami sakon gwamnatin Amurka wanda ke bayyana dabarun sadarwa kuma a bayyane yake ya fito ne daga Kwamitin Tsaro na Kasa, tare da dabarun da aka nakalto a matsayin "Dukkanin China.
An gaya mana mu yi kokarin isar da wannan sakon ta kowace hanya da za mu iya, ta hanyar hada taron manema labarai da kuma nunawa a talabijin". Kafofin yada labarai kamar su Politico, Foreign Policy, da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin China na aikawa da taimako ga kasashen da cutar ta shafa wani bangare ne na farfagandar neman yin tasiri a duniya.
Shugaban harkokin waje na Tarayyar Turai Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "wani bangaren siyasa na kasa, wanda ya hada da yin fada don samun iko ta hanyar karkatar da gaskiya da kuma 'siyasa na jin kai.'"
Borrell ya kuma ce, "China tana tura sakon cewa, ba kamar Amurka ba, tana da abokin tarayya mai dogaro da gaskiya".
China ta kuma yi kira ga Amurka da ta janye takunkumin da ta sanyawa Syria da Venezuela da Iran, kuma an ba da rahoton cewa ta aika da taimako ga kasashen biyu na baya.
An dakatar da kyautar da Jack Ma ya bayar na kayan rufe fuska 100,000 ga Cuba saboda takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya a kan sa a ranar 3 ga Afrilu.
An kuma zargi hukumomin Amurka da karkatar da taimakon da aka bai wa wasu kasashe zuwa kasashensu.
Akwai kuma rikice-rikice game da abin rufe fuska da aka ruwaito tsakanin wasu ƙasashe, kamar Jamus, Austria, da Switzerland; da Jamhuriyar Czech da Italiya.
Bugu da ƙari, Turkiyya ta kwato daruruwan na'urorin sanyaya iska da aka yi niyya don Spain.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta soki rashin hadin kan Tarayyar Turai ga Italiya da cutar ta coronavirus ta shafa.
Maurizio Massari, jakadan Italiya a Tarayyar Turai, ya ce "China ce kawai ke amsawa a kan iyakokin biyu.
Hakika, wannan ba alama ce mai kyau na haɗin kan Turai ba".
A ranar 22 ga Maris, bayan karbar kiran waya daga Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya tura sojojin Rasha don aika da ma'aikatan lafiya na soja, motocin kashe cututtuka na musamman, da sauran kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
Jaridar Italiya La Stampa ta yi kaulin wani "babban jami'in siyasa" da ba a bayyana sunansa ba, wanda ya ce kashi 80 bisa ɗari na taimakon da Rasha ta ba Italiya "ba su da amfani ko kuma ba su da amfani sosai".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da kai hare-hare na "geopolitical da diplomatic".
Shugaban Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, da Ministan Harkokin Wajen Italiya Luigi Di Maio sun yi watsi da rahotannin kuma sun nuna godiyarsu.
Ƙari ga haka, Rasha ta tura jiragen sama masu ɗauke da kayan agaji zuwa Amirka.
