b'Enzyme angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda yake a haɗe zuwa ƙwayoyin waje na waje (cells) a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, kodan, da kuma hanji.
ACE2 tana da ayyukan da suka saba wa angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Angiotensin (1-7), wanda ya sa ya zama kyakkyawan manufa na magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin wurin shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses.
ACE2 na mutum ana kiransa da hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 shine zinc-containing metalloenzyme wanda yake a saman ƙwayoyin endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Sunadaran ACE2 suna da M2 peptidase na N-terminal da kuma C-terminal renal collectrin amino acid transporter.
ACE2 shine furotin mai kulawa na membrane na irin I, tare da yankin da ke aiki da enzymatically wanda aka fallasa a kan sel a cikin huhu da sauran kwayoyin.
Rukunin ACE2 na waje an cire shi daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme, wanda aka sani da sheddase, kuma ana fitar da sunadarin da aka samar a cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan kwayoyin halitta: ACE2 yana haɗe da ƙwayoyin cuta musamman ƙwayoyin alveolar na huhu na II, ƙananan ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin endothelial na jijiyoyi da jijiyoyin jini, da ƙwayoyin tsoka na jijiyoyin jini a cikin mafi yawan kwayoyin halitta.
Hakanan an sami bayyanar ACE2 mRNA a cikin cortex na kwakwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine a matsayin mai daidaita ACE.
ACE tana rushe angiotensin I hormone zuwa angiotensin II na vasoconstrictor.
A ƙarshe, ACE2 ta yanke amino acid na karboxyl na phenylalanine na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ta yi amfani da shi don zama angiotensin (1-7) vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg -Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya karya wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorfin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana tsara zirga-zirgar membrane na aminogin amino acid mai tsaka-tsaki SLC6A19 kuma yana da hannu a cikin cututtukan Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin na transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babbar hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses, wanda ya haɗa da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ɗaurewar furotin S1 a kan SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 spike da enzyme ACE2 a kan farfajiyar sel yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma fassarar ƙwayoyin cuta da enzymes zuwa cikin endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Wannan shigarwar kwayar cutar kuma tana buƙatar samar da furotin S ta TMPRSS2 mai hana serin protease, wanda aka hana shi a halin yanzu ana bincika shi azaman magani mai yuwuwa.
Duk da haka, yawancin al'ummomin ƙwararru da ƙungiyoyin tsarawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE da kuma magungunan ARB na yau da kullun.
Binciken da aka yi na yau da kullun da kuma nazarin meta, wanda aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "amfani da ACE inhibitors ya haifar da raguwar 34% a cikin haɗarin cutar huhu idan aka kwatanta da iko".
Bugu da ƙari, "amfani da ACE inhibitors kuma yana rage haɗarin cutar huhu a cikin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da haɗarin haɗarin cutar huhu, musamman marasa lafiya da ke fama da bugun jini da rashin cin nasara na zuciya.
Amfani da ACE inhibitors kuma yana da alaƙa da raguwar mutuwar cututtukan huhu, kodayake sakamakon ba shi da ƙarfi idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin huhu gaba ɗaya".
Ana sa ran sake haɗuwa da ACE2 na ɗan adam (rhACE2) ya zama sabon magani don raunin huhu mai tsanani, kuma ya bayyana yana haɓaka haemodynamics na huhu da iskar oxygen a cikin aladu tare da cutar cututtukan cututtukan huhu mai tsanani wanda lipopolysaccharides ke haifar.
Rayuwar rhACE2 a cikin mutum yana da kimanin sa'o'i 10 tare da tsawon aiki na minti 30 ban da tsawon sakamako (tsawon) sa'o'i 24.
Wasu binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai alƙawarin marasa lafiya tare da rashin haƙuri ga magungunan tsarin renin-angiotensin na gargajiya (RAS inhibitors) ko a cikin cututtuka tare da angiotensin II a cikin hawan jini.
