Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020 cewa sunan cutar a hukumance shine "COVID-19".
Shugaban WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ya bayyana cewa CO na nufin corona, VI na nufin kwayar cutar, D na nufin cuta, da kuma 19 na nufin lokacin da aka fara gano cutar: 31 ga Disamba, 2019.
